room_title: Escape room "The Wizarding School" by Quest Factor in Seattle
review: The detail and creativity of the Escape Room was very very impressive. A very enjoyable evening. Funny thing is that I don't think that we would have solved the Room without the creative thinking of two of the kids. Not kidding!

room_title: Escape room "The Wizarding School" by Quest Factor in Seattle
review: Unique and challenging puzzles. Nice environment with free coffee and gaming beforehand. Would defo recommend.

room_title: Escape room "The Wizarding School" by Quest Factor in Seattle
review: This place is great. Rooms have. Good variety of puzzles that are all executed well. I have done a few rooms with this company and have been impressed with them all.
